folder: Kings Highway & Snyder Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
King's Highway, (rear view) between Snyder (right) and Tilden Aves., looking westward. On the east side of King's Highway, from left to right, are the homes of P. Remsen (1873) and T.S. Remsen (1860-1873); between them in the backgrodnd are Nos. 280-282 East 56th Street. To the left of the P. Remsen house, is a 2 1/2 story house; which is No. 316 East 56th Street.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
